<dt>nice_code_layout 
 </dt>
<dd>

<b>Shortcoming:</b> You're not using the CPANTS-recommended way of coding, which looks like<pre>
;my $foo
;if ($foo){
 ;$bar=$foo
 ;$bar**2
}else{
 ;$bar=42}
</pre><br>
<b>Remedy:</b> Do not listen to crazy Australians!<br>

